{{Infobox language |name=Cwi Bwamu |nativename=Bwamu Twĩ |region=[[Burkina Faso]] |ethnicity=[[Bwa people|Bwa]], Tara |speakers=24,000 |date=1999 |ref=e18 |familycolor=Niger-Congo |fam2=[[Atlantic–Congo languages|Atlantic–Congo]] |fam3=[[Gur languages|Gur]] |fam4=Northern Gur |fam5=[[Bwa languages|Bwa]] |iso3=bwy |glotto=cwib1235 |glottorefname=Cwi Bwamu }}
'''Cwi Bwamu''', or simply '''Cwi''' (Twĩ), is a [[Gur language]] of [[Burkina Faso]].
